# =====================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES
# =====================================

# 1. The archive/ directory contains migrated configs and should be in version control
# 2. But exclude runtime-generated files from archive/ subdirectories
# 3. Keep .gitignore file itself under version control
# 4. Use `git add -f` to force-add specific files if needed
# 5. Large data files and logs should never be in git


